I was an asshole.

521
00:20:45,661 --> 00:20:46,628
Pardon my French.

522
00:20:46,662 --> 00:20:49,714
I don't mind your French.

523
00:20:49,749 --> 00:20:51,950
It's come to my attention
that I may have let

