00:21:27,753 --> 00:21:31,656
We were trying
to find a cure.

538
00:21:31,674 --> 00:21:34,325
And we failed.

539
00:21:34,343 --> 00:21:36,511
You never cared
about the money.

540
00:21:36,546 --> 00:21:39,798
The only money
I cared about is

541
