but I know how it feels
to think that you did.

551
00:22:01,954 --> 00:22:05,207
And I have a way to make sure
that neither one of us

552
00:22:05,241 --> 00:22:07,492
feels that way again.

553
00:22:07,526 --> 00:22:09,527
So your great plan
backfired.

554
00:22:09,545 --> 00:22:11,195
Harvey, I'm sorry.

555
00:22:11,214 --> 00:22:12,297
I don't need you to say
I'm sorry.

556
00:22:12,331 --> 00:22:13,665
But the next time
I tell you to sit tight,

557
