- Well, then we're screwed.

592
00:23:31,243 --> 00:23:33,128
But that's not gonna happen.

593
00:23:33,162 --> 00:23:34,779
Look, Donna.

594
00:23:34,797 --> 00:23:38,249
I am trying so hard
to be brave.

595
00:23:38,283 --> 00:23:39,784
But what if Louis ends up
finding out

