00:23:52,348 --> 00:23:53,982
ordered multiple murders.

603
00:23:54,016 --> 00:23:56,318
Harvey said he'd fix it.

604
00:23:56,352 --> 00:23:58,469
Two days later,
that partner was in prison.

605
00:23:58,487 --> 00:24:01,139
Stephen was a criminal.
This is an academic.

606
00:24:01,157 --> 00:24:02,907
He hasn't done
anything wrong.

