00:24:02,942 --> 00:24:04,693
Well, what makes Harvey great
at his job is he knows

608
00:24:04,744 --> 00:24:06,828
that everybody
has done something wrong.

609
00:24:06,862 --> 00:24:10,832
Even the most esteemed
ethics professor in the country?

610
00:24:10,866 --> 00:24:12,117
The cleaner they look,

611
00:24:12,151 --> 00:24:14,452
the more dirt
they've swept under the rug.

612
00:24:14,486 --> 00:24:16,588
I'm telling you,
Harvey's gonna walk in there,

613
00:24:16,622 --> 00:24:17,956
he's gonna find the lump,

614
00:24:17,990 --> 00:24:20,759
and Henry Gerard is not
gonna know what hit him.

615
00:24:23,045 --> 00:24:24,462
Wednesday nights,
8:00 to 10:00,

616
00:24:24,496 --> 00:24:26,330
it's like clockwork.

617
00:24:26,349 --> 00:24:28,350
Consistency is nothing
to be feared.

618
00:24:28,384 --> 00:24:31,502
I wasn't afraid of it.
I was counting on it.

619
00:24:31,520 --> 00:24:33,521
Mr. Specter.

620
00:24:33,556 --> 00:24:35,023
Professor Gerard.

621
00:24:35,057 --> 00:24:37,308
Looks the same
as the last time I was here.

