00:24:39,562 --> 00:24:40,845
Yes, you can.

624
00:24:43,149 --> 00:24:44,515
I see
you're as humble as ever.

625
00:24:44,533 --> 00:24:46,701
We'll see who's humble
in a few minutes.

626
00:24:46,736 --> 00:24:48,069
And for the record,

627
00:24:48,120 --> 00:24:50,038
you were wrong
about how I'd turn out.

628
00:24:50,072 --> 00:24:51,539
I know how you turned out.

629
00:24:51,574 --> 00:24:54,709
More settlements than
any other lawyer in New York.

