00:24:54,744 --> 00:24:56,661
More closings than
any other lawyer in New York.

631
00:24:56,695 --> 00:24:58,713
And settling is what it takes
to get the job done

632
00:24:58,748 --> 00:24:59,998
in the real world.

633
00:25:00,032 --> 00:25:01,873
I know what it takes for you
to do what you do,

634
00:25:01,884 --> 00:25:04,035
and compromising your way
through life

635
00:25:04,053 --> 00:25:07,038
is no way to go
about the law.

636
00:25:07,056 --> 00:25:10,508
I see
you're as pompous as ever.

637
00:25:10,542 --> 00:25:12,844
What did you come here for,
Mr. Specter?

638
00:25:12,878 --> 00:25:15,379
- I came to ask for a favor.
