- There isn't.

693
00:27:35,408 --> 00:27:37,192
Well, I refuse
to believe that.

694
00:27:37,243 --> 00:27:38,477
I don't give a shit
what you believe.

695
00:27:38,495 --> 00:27:40,079
Get it through your head.
I'm not superman.

696
00:27:40,113 --> 00:27:43,649
I failed,
and I don't know what to do.

697
00:27:43,667 --> 00:27:45,868
Mike.

698
00:28:06,973 --> 00:28:09,858
Tim, I thought
I was meeting with Lisa.

699
00:28:09,893 --> 00:28:11,560
And I thought
you were above board.

700
00:28:11,611 --> 00:28:13,028
I see you've read
our amendment.

701
00:28:13,063 --> 00:28:15,364
You drafted a provision
that if they didn't spend

702
00:28:15,398 --> 00:28:17,015
$100 million
finishing that drug,

703
00:28:17,033 --> 00:28:19,034
they'd have to pay us
an extra $100 million.

704
00:28:19,069 --> 00:28:20,869
I drafted a provision
to see

705
00:28:20,904 --> 00:28:22,854
if they'd put their money
where their mouth is.

706
00:28:22,872 --> 00:28:24,022
What you did was
what you always wanted to do--

707
00:28:24,040 --> 00:28:25,324
tank this deal.

708
00:28:25,358 --> 00:28:27,710
- They pulled the offer.
- They yanked the offer.

709
00:28:27,744 --> 00:28:30,245
