00:28:42,208 --> 00:28:43,559
and it's not gonna hold up.

717
00:28:43,593 --> 00:28:45,594
It'll hold up just fine.

718
00:28:45,645 --> 00:28:47,212
We'll see.

719
00:28:47,230 --> 00:28:50,149
This is a subpoena.

720
00:28:51,601 --> 00:28:54,019
So the next time
we have this conversation,

721
00:28:54,053 --> 00:28:56,572
