to ask me that.

734
00:29:25,935 --> 00:29:28,020
They're going to ask me
about his condition.

735
00:29:28,054 --> 00:29:30,639
I saw him, Lisa.

736
00:29:30,690 --> 00:29:32,191
I know what he was like.

737
00:29:32,225 --> 00:29:35,093
Quentin knew
what he wanted.

